                     <title xml:lang="he">ספר הנצחון</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Folios 1-3 (flyleaves) contain short descriptions of the work contained in the manuscript, in Latin and English, partly incorrect. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
